ZH: 这个地区的土地非常肥沃。
EN: The soil in this area is very fertile.

ZH: 这个农场的土壤肥沃，适合种植各种蔬菜。
EN: The soil on this farm is fertile and suitable for growing all kinds of vegetables.

ZH: 这片土地过去因为矿产丰富而变得异常肥沃。
EN: This land became exceptionally fertile in the past due to its rich mineral deposits.

ZH: 他们选择在这片肥沃的土地上建立了自己的农场。
EN: They chose to establish their farm on this fertile land.

ZH: 长期的耕作使得这片土地变得更加肥沃。
EN: Long-term cultivation has made this land even more fertile.

ZH: 这片土地可以被称为是肥沃的田园。
EN: This land can be called a fertile countryside.

ZH: 这个地区的气候和土壤条件非常适合农作物生长，所以很肥沃。
EN: The climate and soil conditions in this area are very suitable for crop growth, so it is very fertile.

ZH: 这片土地的水资源充足，使得它变得非常肥沃。
EN: The abundant water resources on this land make it very fertile.

ZH: 这个国家的中部地区是十分肥沃的农业区。
EN: The central region of this country is a very fertile agricultural area.

ZH: 这片肥沃的土地吸引了很多农民前来开垦。
EN: This fertile land has attracted many farmers to come and reclaim it.

ZH: 这片土地在历史上曾是一个非常肥沃的王国。
EN: This land was once a very fertile kingdom in history.

ZH: 他们在这块肥沃的土地上栽种了大量的水果树。
EN: They planted a large number of fruit trees on this fertile land.

ZH: 这片沃土适合种植谷物和蔬菜。
EN: This fertile soil is suitable for growing grains and vegetables.

ZH: 这个省份以其肥沃的土地和富饶的资源而著称。
EN: This province is known for its fertile land and abundant resources.

ZH: 在这片土地上生长的庄稼会比其他地方更加肥沃。
EN: Crops grown on this land will be more fertile than elsewhere.

ZH: 这个地区的土壤富含有机质，非常肥沃。
EN: The soil in this area is rich in organic matter, very fertile.

ZH: 这片沃土适合种植各种作物，它胜过其它地方。
EN: This fertile soil is suitable for growing all kinds of crops, surpassing other places.

ZH: 这片土地的气候适宜，土质肥沃，种植的作物效果非常好。
EN: The climate and fertile soil in this land make the crops planted here very successful.

ZH: 这块肥沃的土地被用来养殖玉米和大豆。
EN: This fertile land is used to farm corn and soybeans.

ZH: 我们要在这片沃土上建立一个现代化的农场。
EN: We are going to establish a modern farm on this fertile land.
